Climate Change ✅
Bringing back manufacturing ✅ Now, student loan relief for those who need it most ✅

@POTUS ran on making meaningful change for Americans from the bottom up and the middle out—and he’s delivered.

@POTUS is right: we need to take action to make our supply chains more resilient.
 
Our supply chains are buckling under surging consumer demand &amp; a global pandemic. It’s critical that we act now. 
https://t.co/kJShf6yMCH

“We must acknowledge that our country is in the midst of a full-blown civics crisis and take decisive action to fix it.”

@RetiredOrrin and I don’t always agree, but on the importance of civics education, he’s right. We cannot wait to invest in civics ed.
